OL,3,CCampaigners petition against plans for
OL,4,Chorse-drawn carriage rides in city
OL,6,FWatch: The idea of horse-drawn
OL,7,Fcarriage rides in Canterbury has
OL,8,Fsparked concern, as Malcolm Shaw
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FMore than 15,000 people have signed a
OL,12,Fpetition opposing the idea of horse-
OL,13,Fdrawn carriage rides through the
OL,14,Fstreets of Canterbury.
OL,16,FThey claim the sightseeing tours would
OL,17,Fbe 'dangerous and cruel', and are
OL,18,Fcalling on the city council to oppose
OL,19,Fthem.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
