OL,3,CCampaigners petition against plans for
OL,4,Chorse-drawn carriage rides in city
OL,6,FIn recent months, posts have appeared
OL,7,Fon social media promoting horse-drawn
OL,8,Fcarriage rides through the Kent city.
OL,10,FThe organisers told ITV Meridian that
OL,11,Fthey envisage two-and-a-half mile
OL,12,Fjourneys, passing four historic sites
OL,13,Fincluding Westgate Towers.
OL,15,FHowever the idea has horrified animal
OL,16,Frights campaigners.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
