FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772048439
OL,3,CCampaigners petition against plans for
OL,4,Chorse-drawn carriage rides in city
OL,6,FReuben Skeats from People for the
OL,7,FEthical Treatment of Animals said:
OL,8,F"Horses aren't taxis. It's not right
OL,9,Fthat four days a week they should be
OL,10,Fliving nose-to-bumper being carted in
OL,11,Fand out of the city, being forced to
OL,12,Fhaul tourists around the city.
OL,14,F"Decent people recognise that they
OL,15,Faren't just there for people to use.
OL,16,FThey are not commodities that we can
OL,17,Fforce to work for our benefit."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
