PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772048439
OL,3,CCampaigners petition against plans for
OL,4,Chorse-drawn carriage rides in city
OL,6,FThe woman behind the idea, Ellie
OL,7,FSamuels from Perfect Pleasure Horse
OL,8,FDrawn Carriages, declined to appear on
OL,9,Fcamera. However she says the welfare
OL,10,Fof her horse is her priority, and that
OL,11,Fshe has chosen a quiet route with
OL,12,Fminimal traffic.
OL,14,FCanterbury City Council says it is in
OL,15,Fdiscussions with the potential
OL,16,Foperator on whether a licence is
OL,17,Fneeded.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
