PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772048439
OL,3,CCampaigners petition against plans for
OL,4,Chorse-drawn carriage rides in city
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "It goes without
OL,7,Fsaying that the welfare of any animals
OL,8,Finvolved would be one of our highest
OL,9,Fpriorities and the process would
OL,10,Finclude a vet's inspection, which our
OL,11,Fanimal welfare officer would also
OL,12,Fattend."
OL,14,FThose in favour of the horse-drawn
OL,15,Fcarriages, which can be found in
OL,16,Fplaces like Bruges in Belgium, say
OL,17,Fthey would be a welcome sight and
OL,18,Fwould encourage tourism. At the same
OL,19,Ftime, campaigners say many other
OL,20,Fcities have banned them on safety and
OL,21,Fwelfare grounds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
